      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LITTLE KADE (2) jumped from a squeeze box last start but was quickly into stride and led throughout to score (18.11) at this track in a Grade 5 over 320m. One of the key runners again. TWELVE MEN (1) was below best at her last start when 6th at Taree Super Track following a second place finish (15.98) at The Gardens two back. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and seven minor placings to her credit. Has ability and is one of the better chances. FAITH IN CAEDEN (3) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished third (16.05) at The Gardens latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Can measure up. WICKED RAVEN (8) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.",
